00736 ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
00737 /// Bit 0: stallGuardTM status
00738 /// (1: threshold reached)
00739 /// Bit 1: Overtemperature
00740 /// (1: driver is shut down due to overtemperature)
00741 /// Bit 2: Pre-warning overtemperature
00742 /// (1: Threshold is exceeded)
00743 /// Bit 3: Short to ground A
00744 /// (1: Short condition etected, driver currently shut down)
00745 /// Bit 4: Short to ground B
00746 /// (1: Short condition detected, driver currently shut down)
00747 /// Bit 5: Open load A
00748 /// (1: no chopper event has happened during the last period with constant coil polarity)
00749 /// Bit 6: Open load B
00750 /// (1: no chopper event has happened during the last period with constant coil polarity)
00751 /// Bit 7: Stand still
00752 /// (1: No step impulse occurred on the step input during the last 2^20 clock cycles)
00753 ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
